# Skill Orchestration

## Superpowers Integration

Superpowers handles **process orchestration** (brainstorming ‚Üí plan ‚Üí execute ‚Üí verify ‚Üí finish). This rule handles **domain-specific skill selection** ‚Äî which project skill to delegate to for a given domain (backend, frontend, DB, security, etc.).

When both apply, Superpowers process skills run first, then delegate domain work to project skills listed below.

## Subagent Strategy

- Use subagents to keep main context window clean
- Offload research, exploration, and parallel analysis to subagents
- One task per subagent for focused execution
- Max 4 concurrent subagents

