## Orchestration Rules

- For multi-skill tasks, read `mission-control` SKILL.md first
- Always read a skill's SKILL.md before delegating to it
- Track orchestration progress in `tasks/todo.md`
- Record failures and lessons in `tasks/lessons.md`
